.Dd September 12, 2016
.Dt NOLOGIN 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm nologin
.Nd politely refuse a login
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
displays a message that an account is not available and
returns a non-zero exit code.
It is intended as a replacement shell field for accounts that
have been disabled.
